"11131de1dd4cb1afbbfa7f4b61ae766943e0417c","tid":2223646,"uid":75823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:32:21.000Z","msg":"我係twitter問反侵人士<br />\n侵輸左佢地12個會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:49:42.000Z","msg":"應該加多句如果你係佢哋家屬，不過邊個嬴咗都好，都係要爭取12港人返返嚟香港同埋得到應有嘅保障+法律程序"},{"pid":"f1ebfbed8513dc75c15a617439c1afd786003eaa","tid":2223646,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:50:07.000Z","msg":"總係有班人坐定碌木咁等人做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2223758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2223758</a>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"f1ebfbed8513dc75c15a617439c1afd786003eaa","tid":2223646,"uid":189650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-30T09:50:07.000Z","msg":"總係有班人坐定碌木咁等人做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2223758\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2223758</a>"}}